com.meta64.mobile.config

Class SessionContext

  • Object
    • SessionContext

  • @Component
 @Scope(value="session",
       proxyMode=TARGET_CLASS)
public class SessionContext
extends Object
    Wrapper for holding variables that we need to maintain server state of for a session. Basic session state storage is all collected here.

    The ScopedProxyMode.TARGET_CLASS annotation allows this session bean to be available on singletons or other beans that are not themselves session scoped.
